content: So with that, for the fourth quarter, we expect total sales of $535 million to $555 million; gross margin rate as a percent of sales to be in the 35.4% to 35.8% range; SG&A as a percent of sales to be in the 32.7% to 33.2% range; an effective tax rate of approximately 25%; and diluted EPS of $0.07 to $0.10. For the full year, we expect total sales of $2.153 billion to $2.173 billion; gross margin rate as a percent of sales to be in the 39.2$ to 39.3% range; SG&A as a percent of sales to be in the 32.3$ to 32.4% range; an effective tax rate of approximately 23%; and diluted EPS of $0.89 to $0.92.
